chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Fine then. I hope you rot in hell until you figure it out.

chat.message: Don't say things like that. You don't mean it.

chat.message: Screw you. You just want to hang out and party with your stupid roommate and hoes all day.

chat.name: Naveed
chat.message: Why even put up with her crazy ass?

chat.name: Naveed

chat.name: Naveed

chat.message: Yeah, but she's just worried because of the distance.

chat.name: Naveed
chat.message: Kash, she would only be worse if you were closer. She's controlling. This is unhealthy. Just block her.

chat.message: Hey

chat.message: I'm sorry about earlier.

chat.message: Really? J Me too. I don't like it when we fight.

chat.message: Me either. It makes me sad when you do things to get me upset like that

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: I honestly don't know when I'm doing it though. I never want to make you feel bad or worried.

chat.message: I know you don't do it on purpose.

chat.message: OMG that doesn't sound good L

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: You can get pretty angry and mean at times.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Yes, but do you understand why?

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: I'm defending myself against the things that you do.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: But I don't see what I'm doing. Surely nothing that deserves you telling me to rot in hell.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Are you serious right now?

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: Yes I am.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: You are always saying things to put me down and I have to end this.

chat.message: I'll kill myself.

chat.message: What?!

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: NO! I definitely don't want that.

chat.message: Then don't leave.

chat.message: That's the only deal I'll make with you.

chat.message: You need serious help then Ash.

chat.message: Kash do you love me?

chat.message: What?

chat.message: Do you freaking love me?

chat.message: Not yet. What are you talking about?

chat.message: Well I love you.

chat.message: It's too soon for that.

chat.message: Never too soon. Are you going to make me do this Kash?

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: Listen to me. I won't be controlled by threats and manipulations anymore.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: If you want me then treat me the way I treat you. But threatening suicide and accusing me of things isn't okay.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Alright. I'm sorry. You don't have to be so harsh.

chat.message: Let's just talk later.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Keep typing or I'll do it.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: You want to see the noose I'm making. Don't do this to me.

chat.message: You're doing this to us. I'm blocking you now.

chat.message: Well that's a bit dramatic.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: You can't go two seconds without being crazy.

chat.name: Ashlyn
chat.message: Wait. Please. I'm sorry. I'll do better. I didn't mean any of it.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: (One Month Later) I don't know if you are allowed to use this app anymore but I hope you're okay now. I guess you may know this but the last time we talked I found a site online that helped people in your area suffering from depression.

chat.name: Kash
chat.message: I sent them the messages and they said they'd send someone over to help right away. Last I heard they sent you to a mental hospital.

chat.message: Please know that I did it because I care.

chat.message: That's what it feels like when someone cares about you, Ashlyn. It should never hurt.

chat.message: Hey there Kash

chat.message: Oh I'm sorry. I've moved on.
